ItemRefItemDef.label: Unique Subject Identifier

ItemRefItemDef.label: Sequence Number
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: Sequential number identifying records within each USUBJID in the domain.

ItemRefItemDef.label: Start Date/Time of Element
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: If Element = SCREEN, derived from SVSTDTC where VISIT = SCREENING or from DS where DSDECOD = 'INFORMED CONSENT', whichever is earliest. If Element = EOS, derived from DS where DSCAT = DISPOSITION EVENT. For treatment Elements, derived from first EXSTDTC for the element. For the complete algorithm see the referenced external document.

ItemRefItemDef.label: End Date/Time of Element
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: If Element = SCREEN, derived from SVENDTC where VISIT = SCREENING. If Element = EOS, derived from DS where DSCAT = DISPOSITION EVENT or from the latest EXENDTC from EX whichever is later. For treatment Elements, derived from last EXENDTC for the element. For the complete algorithm see the referenced external document.

ItemRefItemDef.label: Planned Order of Elements within Arm

ItemRefItemDef.label: Name of Actual Treatment
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: Derived from ARM, ARMCD

ItemRefItemDef.label: Dose per Administration
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: If ARMCD=WONDER10 then EXDOSE = Number of Tablets per Day (QVAL where QNAM=SMNO) * 10. If ARMCD=WONDER20 then EXDOSE = Number of Tablets per Day (QVAL where QNAM=SMNO) * 20. If ARMCD=PLACEBO then EXDOSE = 0.

ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: Derived from ARM, ARMCD - equal to mg

ItemRefItemDef.label: Study Day of Start of Treatment
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: EXSTDY = EXSTDTC - RFSTDTC+1 if EXSTDTC is on or after RFSTDTC. EXSTDTC - RFSTDTC if EXSTDTC precedes RFSTDTC.

ItemRefItemDef.label: Study Day of End of Treatment
ItemRefItemDef.algorithm: EXENDY = EXENDTC-RFSTDTC+1 if EXENDTC is on or after RFSTDTC. EXENDTC - RFSTDTC if EXENDTC precedes RFSTDTC.
